channel.title: Problem with "You cannot tele above Y 3712 wildy."
channel.description:
Well me and my old friend were working on a tutorial and it worked, it was the one that when you ::noclip you get sent to the ship and you can't leave...
Well now when your in the wildy you can't leave, with a command or emote or regular teleport. Now what? Is there a way so my ship stays the same but you can tele out of the wildy?
Thank you,
~Liamsford
REMINDER: Lots of noobs have been posting saying something that dosn't help and hoping they get some rep, more posts, etc. Well please DON'T!
